OL,5, Scotland's largest jail is so          
OL,6, overcrowded and outdated that it could 
OL,7, suffer a "catastrophic failure" at any 
OL,8, time, its governor has said.           
OL,10,FBarlinnie prison in Glasgow is running 
OL,11,Fat 140% capacity with just under 1,400 
OL,12,Fprisoners when it was designed for 987.
OL,14,FA replacement for the 140-year-old jail
OL,15,Fwas due to open in 2025 - but that has 
OL,16,Fbeen pushed back to 2027.              
OL,18,FGovernor Michael Stoney said: "This    
OL,19,Fprison can't last that much longer. The
OL,20,Finfrastructure fails consistently."    
